BeeeOn Emulator


Application emulating end stations in intelligent home system, which are used to measure physical quantities and interact with switches. Application has a comprehensive graphical user interface, which allows testing of other system layers and recording of statistical data about emulation contributing to system analysis.

Application was created as bachelor's thesis on FIT VUT in Brno

Author: Filip Sutovsky - xsutov00@stud.fit.vutbr.cz
